      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute perfection. It\u2019s been super well-loved and is still looking great and running like a dream. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for its next big adventure! It\u2019s clean, reliable, and just waiting for a new owner to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
