      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. Mechanically, the car is sorted: the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been reinforced to ensure lateral rigidity under load. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the communicative feedback these M-chassis are known for. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the drivetrain remains tight and the limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up. A mechanically robust example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
